div.span: A full stack web developer from Chicago
div.p: Welcome to my GitHub. I work as a substitute TA at the Northwestern University coding bootcamp and as a grader, learning assistant, and tutor for 2U/Trilogy. I build web apps primarily in MERN stack. I've particularly enjoyed web sockets, animations, and the Web Audio API.
- 🌱 I’m currently learning graphQL, Next, WebRTC
- 🔭 I’m currently working on MERN projects using WebRTC
